No Errors, Won't Drive Java
We’ve programmed our bot and it drove fine on Saturday (Feb 4th), but Monday it would not drive. We have checked the following: Drive Station Connects Joystick Connects No Errors in Code No Errors in Drive Station Wiring Appears Correct Able to Ping the RoboRIO Motor Controllers Register Correctly Robot Mapping Consistent All programmed in java We have a base drive chassis with nothing else at this time. The code is available at the following link: Looking for ideas on what to check next…
